{"triple_norm": ["tank", "stand there", "amoment"], "true_link": {"object": "NULL", "subject": "/m/07cmd"}, "src_sentences": ["Tank stand there a moment", "Scarlet Fox ~Tank mounted the Bike and turned it on spinning the rear wheel before speeding off. The current contract made Tank have to go past the action. As long as no one messed up the trip everything would be okay. Tank would take out the target at all costs. Tapping the side of the HUD in Tanks helmet a timer and a decryption came up saying it was complete. It tuned in to the Chatter being made by the Theocracy. Tank caught something from a few troops talking about a suicide mission for going right to the enemy HQ. The council? Tank owed them a favor so with a double tap to the helmet it began to ring. After a moment a voice came up.~ &quot;this is a secure line reserved for emergency purposes only. Please do not call here again or we shall send an officer to your location to... &quot; ~Tank cut the person off~ Patch me through to the chairman. Its Tank. He will accept my call. ~the person began to protest then another voice came on.~ &quot;Its who? Tank?! Give me that! Tank! Why are you calling me?&quot; Chairman. You bailed me out of a situation awhile back. I owe you. I interecepted a Transmission from the Theocracy. A few soldiers were talking of a mission. Against The Council HQ. I suggest you... &quot;&quot;WHAT?! Tank! Since you owe me I want you to get over here and help defend us!... And I know how you think! We will pay you a large sum As well as the amount promised for what ever contract you might be on at the present time!&quot; ~Tank was silent for a moment but then skidded on the Bike to a halt and spun around before Ridding towards the HQ~ Im on my way.... Only because I owe you. If any of the other council men asked this of me i would of refused.... So you know. ~There was a sigh of relief~ &quot;Your a good man Tank! Ill inform our troops of the attack and to watch out for you! But remember! I am not asking for your help because The Council can not defend this place on our own. Im asking because I no longer want you to be in debt to me! understand?!&quot; ~Tank didnt answer right away, eyes upon the battle not far from the area.~ Understood. I expect payment after the job is done. ~Tank hung up.... -.. if I survive...- thinking silently. Looking up the quickest route to the Council HQ Tank made a turn and headed for the HQ~", "Scarlet Fox ~Tank came to a skidding halt infront of the enemy force approaching the HQ. With a quick turn Tank skidded away from them and to the HQ to find out what they wanted to do about the attack first. Stopping at the front of the HQ and walking in Tank went over to where the Councilman was. Im here. What do you want me... The councilman cut Tank off. &quot;Just go out there with our men and make sure they DO NOT get in!&quot; Tank stood there a moment. Fine.. Tank turned and simply walked out of the Building and stood on the steps of the Council HQ waiting for the enemy to arrive.~"], "triple": ["Tank", "stand there", "a moment"], "kbp_info": [], "entity_linking": {"object": null, "subject": "Scarlet_Fox"}, "_id": 888}
