{"triple_norm": ["itachi", "wink at", "sasuke"], "true_link": {"object": "NULL", "subject": "/m/02p8p45"}, "src_sentences": ["Itachi wink at Sasuke", "Sasuke waited for his brother rather impatiently at counter in front of Tenten. He had finished his session with Sakura and now he was ready to go. Onyx eyes watched as his older brother strolled into the main area of the spa. Itachi winked at Sasuke, pulling out his black leather wallet and stepped in front of him. He ignored the glare that Sasuke was directing towards him as he gave Tenten the amount required for one aroma therapy massage and then handed her an extra hundred dollar bill.", "&quot;Shall we, Sasuke?&quot; Itachi asked, heading over to the door, ready to leave the building and travel back to the office.", "As the two brothers walked out into the parking lot, the hot, unforgiving sun shining down on their pale skin, Sasuke finally spoke. &quot;A hundred dollars, Itachi? What, did he give you a hand job or something?&quot;", "Sasuke&apos;s teeth clenched and he looked down at the floor of the vehicle. Every fiber, every cell of his body wanted to reach over and punch the man sitting next to him in the face, but Sasuke was too smart to act on it. Growing up with Itachi had taught him one thing; that his older was definitely just as powerful as he looked and while Sasuke was sure he could get a few good punches and kicks out of it, he wasn&apos;t going to risk challenging him.", "Sasuke and Itachi from You&apos;re Mine.", "Sasuke and Itachi from You&apos;re Mine.", "Sasuke and Itachi from You&apos;re Mine."], "triple": ["Itachi", "wink at", "Sasuke"], "kbp_info": [], "entity_linking": {"object": "Sasuke_Uchiha", "subject": "List_of_Naruto_antagonists"}, "_id": 8261}
